column2: SELECT   p.objID, p.parentID, p.specObjID, p.ra, p.dec,   s.z,s.zErr,s.zWarning,s.class,  p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z,  p.modelMagErr_u, p.modelMagErr_g, p.modelMagErr_r, p.modelMagErr_i, p.modelMagErr_z,  p.extinction_g,p.extinction_r,  p.flags,  lnLExp_r,LnLDev_r,  dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,  p.fracDev_r,p.expAB_r,p.expRad_r,  g.h_alpha_eqw,g.sigma_balmer FROM ..SpecObj as s JOIN ..PhotoObj AS p ON s.bestObjID = p.objID  JOIN dbo.fGetObjFromRect(#,#,#,#) AS b ON s.bestobjid = b.objID  JOIN ..galSpecline as g ON g.SpecObjID = s.SpecobjID WHERE s.z > # AND s.zWarning = #   AND (s.class = &&&)   AND s.z < #   AND ( p.type = # OR p.type = #)   AND p.modelMag_r > # AND p.modelMag_r < #  AND p.expAB_r < #  AND ((p.modelMag_g-p.extinction_g) - (p.modelMag_i-p.extinction_i) < #  AND p.lnLExp_r > (#+p.lnLDeV_r)  AND g.h_alpha_reqw < #  ORDER BY p.ra
